Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:02.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an emergency message \Nfrom the Detention Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:06.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The new Oracion Seis's aim isn't \Nthe destruction of churches!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:09.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're after Celestial Spirit Wizards \Nwho are being sheltered there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:11.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our top priority is finding \Nthem first and protecting them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:15.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly gotten a lot busier around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:50.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! {\i1}Our{\i0} Michelle is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:52.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not definitely an impostor,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:54.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's highly probable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:57.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we've got the real one right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:01.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood! I'll pass it \Non to Master and Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take this girl to a nearby hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:06.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:07.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:10.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we've got to contact \NNatsu and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:12.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they have long-distance \Ncommunication cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:14.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Each team has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:16.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Elfman's got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:21.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible! We got word that the Six \NGenerals are attacking Kardia Cathedral!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:22.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:25.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. None of us are over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:27.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go. Bisca...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:27.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:30.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch Asuka for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:33.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! Lucy! Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:36.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle is an impostor! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:41.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Can you hear me?! Somebody answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:47.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Super! Hot! Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hit the jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:54.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If they go down together, \Nit's convenient for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:57.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, something about it doesn't sit right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:02:58.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, after all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:00.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For what purpose...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:04.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back, Michelle! I \Npromise I'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:08.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been having so much \Nfun playing with you all
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:10.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that I forgot the important \Nwork I have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:12.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:16.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Oracion Seis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:19.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's do this all at once! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:21.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:25.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bombdrop Bonus! Boom-boom-boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:26.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:27.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why destroy the church?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:29.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:31.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:36.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unleashed Despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:40.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:42.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless. I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:49.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:51.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:54.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the idea from Sugar Boy's mucus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:56.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:04:01.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. I can hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:05.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:13.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You make me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:16.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Making like you have a \Nbeautiful friendship...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:17.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cubelious is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:23.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer have any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:28.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that... Your sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:34.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But people can get stronger \Nby overcoming their sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:36.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As if you know anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:40.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can comprehend \Nthe pain that's in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:41.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:45.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone bears pain in their heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:03.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We found the Celestial Spirit Wizard \Nand have her in protective custody!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:05.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Take her to headquarters, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been so busy here, \NI forgot my purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:14.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Titania. One of these days, \Nwe'll settle this for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:23.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:27.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I found him. I captured the \NCelestial Spirit Wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Anti-Link amplitude limiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:31.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to activate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:33.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:34.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:41.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you sever my biological \Nlink, there are more of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:48.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the information he \Ngot out of Father Fabrizio...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:50.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...there are two left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:53.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! What fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:56.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, our prayers will be answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your doctrine is being misused?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:04.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:06.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I explain that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...let's fight one more time, Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:12.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:13.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some kind of doubt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand how males think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:26.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, \Nthe misuse of your doctrine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Zentopia plotting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we departed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:37.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cardinal Rapowant gave \Nus individual missions!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rapowant?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:46.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cardinal... That's one of the \Nchurch's head honchos, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:49.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dan and Mary were to interfere with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:52.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar Boy was to stand by, prepared \Nin case of an emergency...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:53.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Gatman...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:54.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:57.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like the newcomer. In Coco's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:01.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Did something happen to Coco?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:04.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She was imprisoned as a traitor to Legion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:05.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She backed you people up or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:12.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I don't know about the \Nmission that Gatman was given.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a really bad feeling about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my calculations,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:22.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,when that Cleaner came out, it meant there's \Na disturbing movement within Zentopia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:23.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:26.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She told him she hates cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:30.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was rejected? Lily wears \Nhis broken heart on his sleeve...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:33.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interrupt the conversation \Nwith a cooked-up drama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:35.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one more thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:41.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The strange mission Byro-sama \Nand I were given!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:42.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:48.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The order itself, but most especially, we \N{\i1}weren't{\i0} told to get the Infinity Clock back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:52.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though stopping them is the \Nmost important thing right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:56.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:59.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we need to join forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:04.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you came here to look to \NCarla's precognition for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:07.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with all this, Byro-sama's \Nallegiance hasn't crumbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:09.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:13.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a worthier \Nopponent last time, Sammy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:17.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your techniques were aimless and misguided!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:20.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never be able to beat me that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:25.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, you need to get rid of the \Nhesitation that's in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:33.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:36.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still stand, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:42.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly man. No matter how many times you \Nattack, the outcome will be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:48.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:52.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't... No wizard can beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:09:00.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In my Phantom Lord days, maybe \NI would've given up already,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:05.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but unfortunately for you, \NI'm a Fairy Tail wizard now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:09.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you beat the crap outta me, \Nmy heart won't break that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Juvia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:16.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for buying some time, Gajeel-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia has recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:23.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? You think this will snare me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:25.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia won't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:28.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary! Scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:31.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:36.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What is this?! You're \Ngetting tangled up with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:38.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you let go of me, you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:40.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia won't let go! Juvia will endure this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:41.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:42.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Comin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:47.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You scatter, son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:48.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:51.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The timing could've been \Na little better, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:54.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it had been Gray-sama, the \Ntiming would've been perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:55.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:10:00.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible. They took down \NGatman the Cleaner...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:04.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up! How long are \Nyou gonna sleep, Erigor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:06.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be that violent with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:08.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta ask him this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:12.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Tell us what your aim is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:13.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the Infinity Clock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:22.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I was in a \Ndaze... What was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:27.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You just got your memories back, so \Nyou must not be thinking clearly yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in prison before...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:34.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. When was it... \NI had a hideous nightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:38.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like somebody \Nsneaked into my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:43.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I acted as the Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:46.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sneaked into your dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:50.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it was probably a kind of magic \Nthat uses dreams to control people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:57.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Little by little, it must have influenced his \Nbrainwaves and then controlled his unconscious mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:00.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I did as I was told, offering up my memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:03.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and in exchange received the magic power \Nof mastery over weather phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:09.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But forgetting everything... was painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:14.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the hardest thing I've ever been \Nthrough. Mighty power comes at a high price,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:16.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:21.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I heard your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:26.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of throwing in \Nwith you, but let me be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:28.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:30.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:36.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When Cana used divination to decide \Nthese teams, she said something...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:39.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She said, "I don't know \Nwhy, but I'm so sleepy..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:44.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then unbeknownst to her, Cana-san was \Nalso manipulated through her dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:49.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So right from the start, we were paired \Nup into teams that were favorable to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:50.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:53.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We fell right into a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:06.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Befitting of well-known Celestial \NSpirit Wizard, Will Neville...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:10.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in death, he's protected \Nby powerful magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:13.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that effect is about to run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:19.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what your goal is, we're \Nnot going to let you accomplish it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:21.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've sniffed me out already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:23.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:26.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brain II of the new Oracion Seis, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:28.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:36.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?! Omnidirectional Expansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:38.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:46.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Al! Hang in there just a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:51.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:55.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One shot, one down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:03.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bisca!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:04.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a good shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:07.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But she lacks the resolve to shoot someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:12.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to achieve something, \Nyou have to pay a high cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lacking in readiness to lose something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, three in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:25.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-Link activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:33.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard, what did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:36.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that doesn't \Nconcern you, Byro-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:40.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do is carry \Nout your mission, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:41.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:43.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} your opponent here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:48.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Your old pal, Lightning Bonus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:50.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:53.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sin of attacking a church is too serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Talons of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:14:00.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?! Now I \Ncan't use my Slot Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:02.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did my identity go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:04.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was finally able to hit you, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm gonna pay you back \Nfor everything up to now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:11.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wing Slash of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:12.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:21.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this... feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:24.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a really bad feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.37,0:14:26.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san... It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:29.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The scream we heard came from over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:38.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:42.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Cobra do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:49.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Celestial Spirit Wizards' \NAnti-Link is complete?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:53.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:56.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The severing of the biological link.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:58.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Neville,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:01.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the amplitude limiters \Nhave all been unleashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The nightmare that you saw is now going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It will blanket the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:14.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The chaos that had been sealed away \Nis now unleashed upon the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:17.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the beginning of the nightmare \Nthat can never be awakened from!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:25.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The end is in our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:29.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The end is in our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:56.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? What kind of a joke is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:58.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of bells...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unleashing the Infinity Clock...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:04.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the clock? It's too damn big!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:09.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Infinity Clock was hidden \Nright over Zentopia Cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:11.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:17.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the starting point of the doctrine \Nthat was sealed away from Zentopia history.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:21.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The intersection between the beginning \Nand end of goodwill and malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:28.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has gone as Cardinal Rapowant \Nas well as the archbishop have commanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:34.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what their real intentions \Nare and it isn't necessary to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:38.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of the doctrine, \Nfor the sake of Zentopia...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We won.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:45.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that! It's a fish! Though \Nit doesn't look good to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So we were too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:50.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While I was wavering, {\i1}this{\i0} happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:52.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Sammy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zentopia Cathedral!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:16:59.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to confirm the \Ntruth with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:04.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! We haven't heard yet what \Nkind of order you and Byro got!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:07.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sammy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:09.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Infinity Clock has begun to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:39.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! We have to do something to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have my own mission to carry out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:47.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's to bring you back \Nwith me, Lucy Heartfilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:52.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! After all this, what \Ndo you want with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:54.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:57.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's my duty to obey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gettin' Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:00.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have the time for this right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:03.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see what's over us?! What \Nare you talking about, mission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:08.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you must know what you should \Nreally be doing right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:09.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:14.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Byro, what are you hesitating \Nfor? Don't think!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:19.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All you need is the doctrine and loyalty... \NAll you have to do is what you were ordered!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:22.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:24.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were fighting Nirvana...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:26.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Klodoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:33.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was then and am now the seventh member of \NOracion Seis, the brains behind the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:34.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The seventh member?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:38.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, um... Aren't you one member short?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:44.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no longer necessary to hide \Nit anymore. Come, the time is ripe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:49.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw away your temporary form and reveal \Nyour true name right here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:50.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:56.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?! You're just \Ntrying to confuse us again, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:19:01.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is Michelle Lobster! She's like \Na little sister to me! She's family!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:07.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She embarked on a journey to search for me \Nso she could deliver my father's memento!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:14.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I'm not gonna be \Ntaken in by that jerk's baloney!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:20.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:24.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on... Tell me he's lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:26.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:31.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:36.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:39.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:52.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi...chelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:20:03.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm a member of the new Oracion Seis. \NImitatia, mistress of mimicry and deception.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:12.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To gather the scattered pieces of the \NInfinity Clock, we needed all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:17.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came to you, \NNee-san, as "Michelle Lobster".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:22.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:26.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We attacked those churches
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:30.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to destroy the biological links \Nthat were spread all over
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:33.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and to release the sealed-up Infinity Clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:40.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With that accomplished now, we \Nonly need you, Lucy-nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:42.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:46.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see! You're being manipulated by magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:48.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:50.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:56.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was all a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:20:59.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:01.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:03.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:10.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly a sneak attack?! That's our girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:15.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Byro, carry out the order \Nyou received from Lapowant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:18.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Lucy Heartfilia back with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:21.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to tell me my orders, wench.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:24.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm loyal to Zentopia's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:28.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's the archbishop's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:33.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever holds that gold seal has the \Nsame authority as the archbishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:37.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware that my orders are \Nthe archbishop's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:41.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your wish is my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:45.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be dangerous to let that man live.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:48.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. We're going to bring him back as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.83,0:21:51.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll be of some use, \Nas a hostage if nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:54.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. As it pleases you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:58.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, mercy is forbidden, Imitatia-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:00.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:04.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Michelle... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:07.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...chelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? There was one \Nmore here. Did he escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:18.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I can't hear you well... \NExplain it one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:21.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.41,0:23:57.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.43,0:23:59.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual. You always sleep like a log.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:01.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, I've had trouble fallin' asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:04.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep havin' these weird dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.27,0:24:05.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nightmares? You, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.72,0:24:08.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that reaction?! Is somethin' funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.24,0:24:13.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm moved that you have that \Nkind of sensitivity, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.07,0:24:16.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Real Nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.67,0:24:19.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'm gonna show you \Nwhat a real nightmare is!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:22.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-W-Wait! We can talk this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.99,0:24:24.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I don't have that kind of sensitivity!
